 },
 {
  "text": "Hi Estephano! I want to cook lunch. Do we have any rice?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a6_hi_estephano_i_want_to_cook_lunch_do_we_have_any.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi Sara! Yes, we have some rice and some vegetables.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a6_hi_sara_yes_we_have_some_rice_and_some_vegetable.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Good! Do we have any eggs? I need three eggs.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a6_good_do_we_have_any_eggs_i_need_three_eggs.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "No, we don't have any eggs. But we have some bread.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a6_no_we_don_t_have_any_eggs_but_we_have_some_bread.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "OK. Can you buy some eggs and some juice at the market?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a6_ok_can_you_buy_some_eggs_and_some_juice_at_the_m.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Sure! We don't have any water too. I can buy some water.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a6_sure_we_don_t_have_any_water_too_i_can_buy_some.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Can I have some coffee, please?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a6_can_i_have_some_coffee_please.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "The food is delicious.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a6_the_food_is_delicious.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi, I am Lucas. Let me tell you about my kitchen. I always have some rice and some bread at home. In the morning, I eat two eggs and I drink some coffee. I do not have any juice today, so I drink water. I like vegetables, so I always buy some at the market. But I do not have any apples now. This weekend, I want to buy some fruit and cook a big meal for my friends.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a6_listening_lucas_food.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hello, my name is Mia. I want to tell you about my favorite cafe in Sao Paulo. Every morning, I order some coffee and some bread with eggs. The coffee there is very good. They do not have any juice, but they have a lot of water and tea. At lunch, I eat some rice with vegetables. I do not eat any meat, so I always choose the vegetables. The food is fresh and delicious. I am very happy when I go there.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a6_listening_mia_cafe.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Estephano wants to cook lunch with Sara. He looks in the kitchen. He has some rice but he does not have any eggs. He makes a shopping list. He goes to the market and buys some eggs and some juice.",
